TNK-BP’s independent directors have
appointed Perella Weinberg Partners, a financial advisory firm,
and Macfarlanes, a law firm, to advise them on on  BP Plc ’s
Arctic exploration deal, Sky News reported.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
